        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "### How to Register for BE-Alert\n1. Visit the [BE-Alert website](https://www.be-alert.be/) and complete the registration form.\n2. Provide your email address to receive a confirmation email.\n3. Create a personal password.\n4. Enter your address and verify its accuracy on the map.\n5. Confirm your registration via the email sent by BE-Alert by clicking the provided link.\n6. Complete your profile:\n   - Select your language preference.\n   - Indicate if you are deaf or hard of hearing.\n   - Provide additional contact details (phone, email) or a secondary address for alerts.\n\nIf you do not have internet access, contact your municipality for assistance with registration."
